  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nRe-write the Eth2.0 libp2p RPC protocol to support request/response handling as outlined here: https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/1158\r\n\r\nThis involves opening a substream per-request, waiting for a varied number of responses (we will use a tokio codec) before closing the substream.\r\n\r\nShift the decoding up from the libp2p layer into the beacon-chain for efficiency.\r\n",
